+	Inserting Objects:
	-	Use this syntax if you need to insert an image:
	```typ
	#figure(
		image("IMAGE_NAME.EXT", width: 100%),
		caption: [IMAGE_CAPTION],
	) <fig:LABEL>

	@fig:LABEL shows an image.
	```
	-	Use this syntax if you need to draw a table:
	```typ
	#figure(
		table(
			columns: 4,
			[Row 1], [a], [b], [c],
			[Row 2], [1], [2], [3],
  	),
  	caption: [Results],
	) <tab:LABEL>

	@tab:LABEL displays some results.
	```

